data.description: This home is very private and cannot be viewed from the road. There is also an electronic gate and the entrance to the driveway. The house has three bedrooms, two up and one on the main floor. There are also two full baths. Both bedrooms upstairs have private covered balconies. There is an excellent view from multiple rooms. The home is nestled on 11 acres, and with over 2600 sq. ft., a huge family room with a burning fireplace and a great view of the lake is very comfortable and inviting. The large kitchen has plenty of counter space and cabinets and is open to the vast dining area. This property has plenty of room for you to spread your wings. The detached garage/shop is 30x50 with concrete floors, electric, and wood heat. The seller just dug a large pond, and there is a pasture area and a round pen. The property is very level and easy to navigate. There is an attached greenhouse with water & 2 additional greenhouses w/ a watering system. Garden area is waiting for your green thumb.
